---
layout: layout.njk
pagination:
  data: news
  size: 1
  alias: article
permalink: "/news/{{ article.slug }}/index.html"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ article.title }}"
---
{% from "components.njk" import breadcrumb %}
<article class="container-keishin py-8 md:py-12 max-w-4xl">
  {{ breadcrumb([{ label: "お知らせ", url: "/news/" }, { label: article.title }]) }}
  <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-3">{{ article.date }} / {{ article.category }}</p>
  <h1 class="section-title">{{ article.title }}</h1>
  <div class="card mt-8 space-y-4">
    <p>{{ article.summary }}</p>
    <p>本文テンプレートです。実運用時はMarkdownまたはCMS連携で本文を更新してください。</p>
    <img src="/assets/images/original/img_bnr-group.jpg" alt="お知らせイメージ" width="950" height="394" class="rounded-2xl w-full object-cover" loading="lazy"/>
  </div>
  <a href="/news/" class="inline-block mt-6 text-brand-700 font-semibold">← お知らせ一覧に戻る</a>
</article>